text: Pennsauken may refer to the following in New Jersey: ==Communities== * Pennsauken Township, New Jersey, in Camden County ==Schools== * Pennsauken High School * Pennsauken Public Schools * Pennsauken Technical High School ==Streams== * Pennsauken Creek, a tributary of the Delaware River ==Train stations== * Pennsauken Transit Center * Pennsauken-Route 73 (River Line station) * 36th Street (River Line station)
title: Pennsauken
